google_879.nl_query: For the driver who set the fastest lap speed, what is his nationality? the fastest lap speed refers to (MAX) fastestLapSpeed;
google_879.golden_query: SELECT T1.nationality FROM drivers AS T1 INNER JOIN results AS T2 ON T2.driverId = T1.driverId ORDER BY T2.fastestLapSpeed DESC LIMIT 1
sparksql_query: SELECT T2.nationality FROM results AS T1 INNER JOIN drivers AS T2 ON T1.driverId = T2.driverId ORDER BY CAST(T1.fastestLapSpeed AS DOUBLE) DESC LIMIT 1

google_1429.nl_query: What is the name of the social event that was attended by the vice president of the Student_Club located at 900 E. Washington St.? name of social event refers to event_name where type = 'Social'; 'Vice President' is position; located at refers to location
google_1429.golden_query: SELECT T2.event_name FROM attendance AS T1 INNER JOIN event AS T2 ON T2.event_id = T1.link_to_event INNER JOIN member AS T3 ON T1.link_to_member = T3.member_id WHERE T3.position = 'Vice President' AND T2.location = '900 E. Washington St.' AND T2.type = 'Social'
